# CyberSec AI Terminal - Environment Variables

# VirusTotal API Key
# Get your free API key at: https://www.virustotal.com/gui/my-api-key
# Free tier: 500 requests/day, 4 requests/minute
VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY=your_virustotal_api_key_here

# Hybrid Analysis API Key
# Get your free API key at: https://www.hybrid-analysis.com/profile/api
# Free tier: 25 analyses/day, 5 analyses/minute
HYBRID_ANALYSIS_API_KEY=your_hybrid_analysis_api_key_here

# Note: MalwareBazaar and URLhaus do not require API keys

# IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# - Never commit actual API keys to version control
# - Never share your API keys
# - Rotate keys if compromised
# - Monitor your API usage to avoid exceeding limits